messages.message: Do we generally have a good idea of the exact days that UAT will occur? I know it happens ~ every two weeks but it doesn't seem to be on the same day, just thinking it would be nice to have on the calendar as a heads up once we know of a certain day.

I want to change this to:
```
Monday: Wrap coding by noon PST.
                 Start UAT at 2 PM PST.
Tuesday: Finish UAT by 2 PM PST.
                Prepare deployments for all clients.```
